<h2>Research Interests</h2>
<ul>
<li><p>Coding for Distributed Storage Systems</p>
</li>
<li><p>Statistical Machine Learning</p>
</li>
<li><p>Information Theory</p>
</li>
<li><p>Performance Analysis of Coded Storage Systems</p>
</li>
<li><p>Coding for Fault Tolerant Computation</p>
</li>
</ul>
